			<h4><a rel="nofollow" id="comment_link_64641152" name="comment_link_64641152" href="//news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23394484&amp;cid=64641152" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64641152)" >The primary gap is in hiring.</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64641152" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64641152); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>4</a>, Insightful)</span></h4>
		</div>
		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a rel="nofollow" href="//slashdot.org/~Narcocide">Narcocide</a>  <span class="uid"><a rel="nofollow" href="//slashdot.org/~Narcocide">( 102829 )</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
